@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #F5F5F5
[*] --> Active
Active --> Cancelled : submit
Cancelled --> Pending : cancel
Cancelled : entry / log author
Pending --> Closed : cancel
Pending : entry / log author
Closed --> Archived : submit
Archived --> Delivered : approve
Delivered --> Archived : revert
Delivered --> [*]
@enduml